    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎免费试用 Aquatic Store Simulator 游戏。在这里，您可以访问游戏教程和商店第一天的体验，了解游戏的外观和玩法。如果您喜欢，请将即将推出的完整游戏添加到您的愿望清单中！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过 <strong>Aquatic Store Simulator</strong> 深入充满活力的水生零售世界！接受管理您自己的水下主题超市的挑战，将业务管理与水生生物的美丽融为一体。在货架上摆放奇异的鱼类、装饰品、定价、收款和维护水族馆。运送鱼类、处理交易、确保您的客户满意。自定义和扩展您的商店，成为终极水族企业家。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏪 <strong>管理您自己的水产商店：</strong>建立和定制您的商店，为客户和海洋生物打造一个天堂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/d604033f22f11d478839f8c58ad4f118.poster.avif?t=1730882691\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/d604033f22f11d478839f8c58ad4f118.webm?t=1730882691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/d604033f22f11d478839f8c58ad4f118.mp4?t=1730882691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📦 <strong>产品展示：</strong>战略性地放置商品以吸引顾客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/52f7268b183a3340f165d1ad6063ad51.poster.avif?t=1730882691\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/52f7268b183a3340f165d1ad6063ad51.webm?t=1730882691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/52f7268b183a3340f165d1ad6063ad51.mp4?t=1730882691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💲 <strong>价格设定：</strong>调整价格以优化销售和客户满意度。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐠 <strong>水族馆准备：</strong>设置和维护养鱼的水族馆，确保它们的健康和快乐，与其他超市或宠物店游戏相比，这是一个突出的特点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/d0f0345ef863a35a7325174dbd45e853.poster.avif?t=1730882691\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/d0f0345ef863a35a7325174dbd45e853.webm?t=1730882691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/d0f0345ef863a35a7325174dbd45e853.mp4?t=1730882691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚚 <strong>鱼类配送：</strong>将选定的鱼类配送给顾客，增强他们的购物体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/29843d3cef6c30738d94759ae409610d.poster.avif?t=1730882691\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/29843d3cef6c30738d94759ae409610d.webm?t=1730882691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/29843d3cef6c30738d94759ae409610d.mp4?t=1730882691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏧 <strong>结帐操作：</strong>处理客户交易并准确提供零钱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/6e5275321aa383c9ac1eedfaa27f30e2.poster.avif?t=1730882691\" width=610 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/6e5275321aa383c9ac1eedfaa27f30e2.webm?t=1730882691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251830/extras/6e5275321aa383c9ac1eedfaa27f30e2.mp4?t=1730882691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 <strong>丰富的库存</strong>：利用大约 500 种物品（包括各种鱼和装饰品）来储备您的商店。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>是什么让我们在“市场”模拟游戏中脱颖而出：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有高级水族箱方面的主题超市（繁殖、护理、装饰） </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有形物品的逼真销售体验 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有超过 500 种物品的丰富库存</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将您的商店变成一个繁荣的水上活动中心，成为终极的水族箱企业家。在 Aquatic Store Simulator 中体验商业管理和水下冒险的完美结合！</p>",
